# A simple program to greet the user and introduce humanlang.

print "--- Welcome to humanlang ---"

# Declare a variable with a specific type.
Declare user_name as a String.

# Ask for user input and store it.
Ask "Before we begin, what is your name?" and set the answer to user_name.

# Combine strings by re-using the 'user_name' variable.
Set user_name to "Hello, " + user_name + "! It is nice to meet you."
show me user_name.

print "This language is ready for your commands!"